snippet.title: Soul Devourer Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
You can wishlist now on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2530620?utm_source=youtube

Soul Devourer is a 2D metroidvania action-platformer still in development, and we plan to release the game in late 2025.
